title: Contrastive Learned Self-Supervised Technique for Fatty Liver and Chronic Liver Identification

abstract: Purpose Liver diseases are life-threatening problems when not cured in time. The root of the prevention lies in the early identification of fatty liver diseases, which may be one of the primary causes of most chronic liver diseases. Computer-aided …
